<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.1.3">
<l>tuṉṉumā maṇimuṭimēl tuḻāyalaṅkal tōṉṟumā leṉkiṉ ṟāḷāl</l>
<l>miṉṉumā maṇimakara kuṇṭalaṅkaḷ vilvīcu meṉkiṉ ṟāḷāl</l>
<l>poṉṉiṉmā maṇiyāra maṇiyākat tilaṅkumā leṉkiṉ ṟāḷāl</l>
<l>kaṉṉimā matiḷpuṭaicūḻ kaṇṇapurat tammāṉaik kaṇṭāḷ kollō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“A garland of tulasī indeed appears on his crown encrusted with great jewels,”</l>
<l rend="indent">she declares;</l>
<l>“His makara earrings, with sparkling great jewels, radiate [like] a rainbow,”</l>
<l rend="indent">she declares;</l>
<l>“Great jewels of gold indeed glitter on his chest, ornamented with sandal paste,”</l>
<l rend="indent">she declares.</l>
<l>Did she see the lord of Kaṇṇapuram encircled on [all] sides by impregnable great walls?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
